text: Woodville is a town in the Tararua District, New Zealand. It is located 75 kilometers north of Masterton and 25 kilometers east of Palmerston North on State Highway 2 and State Highway 3. It once had its own council until 1989. It has a primary school situated in the town. == References == Category:Towns in Horizons Category:Tararua District
title: Woodville, New Zealand
